org.cpsolver.studentsct.online.selection

Class ResectioningWeights

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.cpsolver.studentsct.online.selection.StudentSchedulingAssistantWeights
      • org.cpsolver.studentsct.online.selection.ResectioningWeights
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    SolutionComparator<Request,Enrollment>, StudentWeights

    public class ResectioningWeights
extends StudentSchedulingAssistantWeights
    Re-scheduling variant of StudentWeights model. It is based on the StudentSchedulingAssistantWeights. This model is used when a single course of a student is rescheduled. Following criteria are included:
    • StudentWeights.SameChoiceFactor .. penalization of selecting a different choice (see Choice)
    • StudentWeights.SameRoomsFactor .. penalization of selecting different room
    • StudentWeights.SameTimeFactor .. penalization of selecting different time
    • StudentWeights.SameNameFactor .. penalization of selecting different section (section name / external id does not match)
    Version:
    StudentSct 1.3 (Student Sectioning)
